{
  "tree_id": "writer_scene_002",
  "title": "编剧导出示例 - 地下实验室",
  "description": "模拟编剧导出的实际对白文件，包含各种常见的条件冲突问题",
  "start_node": "n_entrance",
  "nodes": {
    "n_entrance": {
      "node_id": "n_entrance",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你站在地下实验室的金属门前，门上的电子锁闪着红光。空气中弥漫着消毒水和腐烂的混合气味。",
      "next_node": "n_door_choice",
      "fear_intensity": "medium",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "door_unlocked": false,
        "has_access_card": false,
        "power_on": true
      }
    },
    "n_door_choice": {
      "node_id": "n_door_choice",
      "node_type": "choice",
      "text": "你需要打开这扇门，你决定：",
      "choices": [
        {
          "choice_id": "c_search",
          "text": "在附近的尸体上搜索",
          "next_node": "n_search_body"
        },
        {
          "choice_id": "c_force",
          "text": "尝试用蛮力撞开",
          "next_node": "n_force_door"
        },
        {
          "choice_id": "c_hack",
          "text": "尝试破解电子锁",
          "next_node": "n_hack_lock"
        }
      ],
      "fear_intensity": "medium",
      "dialogue_type": "tension"
    },
    "n_search_body": {
      "node_id": "n_search_body",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你强忍着恶心，在腐烂的尸体上翻找。在白大褂的口袋里，你找到了一张门禁卡。",
      "next_node": "n_got_card",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "has_access_card": true,
        "found_body": true
      }
    },
    "n_force_door": {
      "node_id": "n_force_door",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你用肩膀猛撞金属门。门纹丝不动，但你的肩膀剧痛无比。警报声突然响起！",
      "next_node": "n_alarm",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "alarm_on": true,
        "has_access_card": false
      }
    },
    "n_hack_lock": {
      "node_id": "n_hack_lock",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你掏出手机，尝试用自制的破解程序入侵电子锁。屏幕上的数字疯狂跳动...",
      "next_node": "n_hack_result",
      "fear_intensity": "medium",
      "dialogue_type": "tension"
    },
    "n_got_card": {
      "node_id": "n_got_card",
      "node_type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "主角",
      "text": "太好了，有门禁卡了。等等...这张卡上的名字...是陈博士？",
      "next_node": "n_recognize_name",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "variable": "has_access_card",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": true,
          "negation": false
        },
        {
          "variable": "has_access_card",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": false,
          "negation": false
        }
      ],
      "set_variables": {
        "has_access_card": false,
        "found_body": false
      }
    },
    "n_recognize_name": {
      "node_id": "n_recognize_name",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "陈博士是你的导师。五年前，他在这个实验室失踪了。你就是为了找他才来到这里的。",
      "next_node": "n_use_card",
      "fear_intensity": "medium",
      "dialogue_type": "exposition",
      "set_variables": {
        "knows_dr_chen": true,
        "has_access_card": true
      }
    },
    "n_alarm": {
      "node_id": "n_alarm",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "刺耳的警报声在走廊里回荡。你听到深处传来沉重的脚步声，正在快速靠近。",
      "next_node": "n_creature_coming",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "creature_awakened": true,
        "time_remaining": 60
      }
    },
    "n_hack_result": {
      "node_id": "n_hack_result",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "程序成功了！门锁发出咔嗒一声，绿灯亮起。但你注意到屏幕上弹出一条警告：「安全协议已激活」。",
      "next_node": "n_enter_lab",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "door_unlocked": true,
        "security_alert": true
      }
    },
    "n_use_card": {
      "node_id": "n_use_card",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你把门禁卡插到读卡器上。屏幕显示：「身份验证通过。欢迎回来，陈博士。」门缓缓打开。",
      "next_node": "n_enter_lab",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "variable": "has_access_card",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": true,
          "negation": false
