    "n_check_console": {
      "node_id": "n_check_console",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "控制台上显示着所有实验体的状态。大部分是「已终止」，只有实验体-007显示「活动中」。你认出了那个编号...是你失踪的妹妹。",
      "next_node": "n_reveal_truth",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "knows_truth": true,
        "sister_alive": true
      }
    },
    "n_read_report": {
      "node_id": "n_read_report",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "实验报告详细记录了五年前的事故。陈博士为了复活死去的女儿，进行了非法的人体实验。而你，也是实验的一部分。",
      "next_node": "n_reveal_truth",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "exposition",
      "set_variables": {
        "knows_truth": true,
        "is_experiment": true
      }
    },
    "n_hide_room": {
      "node_id": "n_hide_room",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你冲进一个房间，关上门躲在桌子后面。脚步声在门外停了下来。你听到低沉的嘶吼声...",
      "next_node": "n_ending_hide",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "variable": "found_body",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": true,
          "negation": false
        },
        {
          "variable": "found_body",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": false,
          "negation": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "n_face_creature": {
      "node_id": "n_face_creature",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你转身面对黑暗中的身影。当它走入灯光下，你惊呆了...是陈博士。但他已经...不再是人类了。",
      "next_node": "n_ending_face",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension",
      "set_variables": {
        "found_dr_chen": true,
        "is_alive": true,
        "is_dead": true
      }
    },
    "n_run_away": {
      "node_id": "n_run_away",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "你不顾一切地往走廊尽头跑。但你忘记了，门已经被你锁上了...",
      "next_node": "n_dead_end_run",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "tension"
    },
    "n_reveal_truth": {
      "node_id": "n_reveal_truth",
      "node_type": "narration",
      "text": "所有的记忆碎片拼合在一起。你终于想起了一切。五年前，是你亲手把妹妹交给了陈博士...",
      "next_node": "n_ending_truth",
      "fear_intensity": "high",
      "dialogue_type": "exposition",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "variable": "knows_truth",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": true,
          "negation": false
        },
        {
          "variable": "doesnt_know_truth",
          "operator": "==",
          "value": true,
          "negation": false
        }
      ],
      "set_variables": {
        "has_memory": true,
        "guilty": true,
        "has_memory": false
      }
